1. *Čaša* je na stolu. (The *glass* is on the table.)
2. Ovaj *čašu* mi je dao moj prijatelj. (My friend gave me this *glass*.)
3. Kupila sam tri *čaše*. (I bought three *glasses*.)
4. Možete li doneti još jednu *čašu* vode? (Can you bring me another *glass* of water?)
5. *Čaše* su napravljene od stakla. (*Glasses* are made of glass.)
6. Želim da *čaša* bude puna do vrha. (I want the *glass* to be full to the top.)
7. Vidim da su *čaše* prljave, moramo ih oprati. (I see that the *glasses* are dirty, we need to wash them.)
8. *Čaše* se često koriste za piće. (*Glasses* are often used for drinking.)
9. Kada je slavio rođendan, polomio je sve *čaše* u kući. (When he was celebrating his birthday, he broke all the *glasses* in the house.)
10. Spremila sam sok u *čašu* s ledom. (I poured the juice into a *glass* with ice.)

Note: The word "čaše" is the plural form of "čaša", which means "glass" in English. The words in bold indicate the form of the word "čaše" used in each sentence.